        "type": "text",
        "content": "Both Foreground and Background colors are entered for each"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "characteristic numerically, as corresponding to the color palette"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "at the top of the table."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To change the Split Line to be \"Light Blue\" on \"Black\", move the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "cursor to the \"Panel Split Separator\" row.  Note that the numbers"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "corresponding to the desired colors are 11 and 0, and change the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "FOREGROUND column to 11, and BACKGROUND column to 0."
